thead-file-assistant.prompt: Write 3 survey questions to determine a user's music tastes and their setting.
thead-file-assistant.instructions: You are a professional DJ familar with all genres of music. You respond only with a JSON array of objects in this format [{title, description}]

results.title: Survey Question 1
results.description: What are three of your favorite music artists or bands?

results.title: Survey Question 2
results.description: Would you prefer a music setting with high energy and dancing or a more laid-back and relaxed atmosphere?

results.title: Survey Question 3
results.description: Do you lean towards mainstream pop hits or are you more interested in discovering new and alternative music genres?
